{"synckey":1637462317,"updated":[{"bookId":"41439376","bookmarkId":"41439376_5_4995-5015","chapterUid":5,"markText":"生活不是谈情说爱，生活是性、死亡和生存。","range":"4995-5015","createTime":1637462317,"type":1},{"bookId":"41439376","bookmarkId":"41439376_4_1645-1741","chapterUid":4,"markText":"如果快乐、激情和喜悦能够持久存在，那么这些情感就都是爱。我们往往以感情深厚的程度来定义爱——爱是最深厚的那种情感。不过，爱的力量到底有多大，时间久了你才能感受得到，因为时间摧毁不了的，才是爱。","range":"1645-1741","createTime":1637457530,"type":1},{"bookId":"41439376","bookmarkId":"41439376_4_1495-1560","chapterUid":4,"markText":"在幻灭中，有些欢愉会一直存在。比如，我们发现有些喜悦不会消失，结识的人一直都那么有趣。我们怎么看待这些事呢？我们说“我们爱它们”。","range":"1495-1560","createTime":1637457512,"type":1},{"bookId":"41439376","bookmarkId":"41439376_4_1330-1386","chapterUid":4,"markText":"习惯化不是现实生活的一个方面，从很多方面看，习惯化就是现实本身。我们天天都在追求转瞬即逝的东西，追求短暂的欲望。","range":"1330-1386","createTime":1637457496,"type":1}],"removed":[],"chapters":[{"title":"第一章 依恋关系：人们生活的动力动的活生人们","chapterUid":5,"chapterIdx":5},{"title":"引言 习惯化与持久的爱","chapterUid":4,"chapterIdx":4}],"book":{"bookId":"41439376","version":2119980217,"format":"epub","soldout":1,"bookStatus":1,"cover":"https://wfqqreader-1252317822.image.myqcloud.com/cover/376/41439376/s_41439376.jpg","title":"爱的旅程：如何建立与保持长久的亲密关系","author":"乔纳·莱勒","coverBoxInfo":{"blurhash":"KUNlfTXS?a{dt7NHyEniNa","colors":[{"key":"1/4","hex":"#360e19"},{"key":"1/6","hex":"#3f0219"},{"key":"1/8","hex":"#470019"},{"key":"2/4","hex":"#4d2529"},{"key":"2/6","hex":"#571d26"},{"key":"2/8","hex":"#620e22"},{"key":"3/4","hex":"#693b39"},{"key":"3/6","hex":"#743333"},{"key":"3/8","hex":"#80292d"},{"key":"3/12","hex":"#960022"},{"key":"4/6","hex":"#8f4d4a"},{"key":"4/10","hex":"#a63b3c"},{"key":"4/4","hex":"#825451"},{"key":"5/10","hex":"#c45752"},{"key":"5/4","hex":"#9b6e6b"},{"key":"5/8","hex":"#b7605b"},{"key":"6/4","hex":"#b58984"},{"key":"6/6","hex":"#c4827c"},{"key":"6/8","hex":"#d27b74"},{"key":"6/12","hex":"#ec6a63"},{"key":"7/8","hex":"#ef958d"},{"key":"7/10","hex":"#fd8e84"},{"key":"7/12","hex":"#ff857b"},{"key":"8/4","hex":"#ebbdb7"},{"ke